    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining a new-car feel. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment.",
      "price": 49500.0,
